com.ibm.team.repository.common

Interface IBaselineMemberComparison


  • public interface IBaselineMemberComparison
    Expresses the difference in the state of an item between two auditable baselines, referred to as the "prior" baseline and the "after" baseline. The two auditable state handles returned by the methods below are guaranteed to refer to different states of the same item. See IBaselineComparison for more information about comparing two auditable baselines.
    Since:
    0.5
